l_oliveira, a member of ASSEMblergames, give me a little answer/direction :<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent"><br />One of the three ROMs (the first 2MB bank I believe) is connected with a different memory map than that of the other two. I don't remember the details but I believe one of the two banks is connected in mode 20 (lorom) while the other is in mode 21(hirom).<br /></div><br /><br />If anyone here, like kyuusaku understand this and can help me it will be awesome  <img src="http://forums.nesdev.com/images/smilies/icon_confused.gif" alt=":?" title="Confused" /><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4762">ichigobankai</a> — Tue Mar 01, 2011 1:11 am</p><hr />
